dialogue.text: Uh ...? How is it here again?  \nWho are you?

I don't know what the situation is,  \nbut I agreed. My pleasure.
well ...actually I wrote a song,  \nbut I need someone to accompany me chorus, \n is it possible if I ask you to join me?
